# auto-doctor

## Context Profile

Load core workspace policy, harness config, manifests, and platform registration only. Exclude product scenarios, canary, signatures, and learnings.

## Contract

1. Run `auto doctor` with all requested flags unchanged.
2. Inspect canonical source availability, generated surface registration, hooks, plugins, dependencies, and stale manifests.
3. Classify source defects separately from generated/runtime drift and user-owned configuration.
4. Report PASS/WARN/FAIL with exact evidence and safe repair commands.
5. Do not mutate files unless the user explicitly requests repair.
